#Text=The city of Zibo is in Shangdong province in eastern China Image : Immanuel Giel .
#Text=Four dead in Chinese kindergarten school attack
#Text=A man armed with a 2-foot long knife killed three children and a teacher in a brutal attack in Zibo in eastern China .
#Text=The Chinese government has been mostly silent on the incident .
#Text=The man who killed the people was identified as 26 year-old Fang Jiantang , and he later turned himself in to police .
#Text=His motive for killing the children and the teacher is unknown .
#Text=Sources
#Text=Lily Kuo .
#Text=" Four killed in attack on kindergarteners in China " — Los Angeles Times , August 5 , 2010

#Text=The disputed border between Israel and Lebanon is known as the Blue Line ( click to enlarge ) Image : Thomas Blomberg and other Wikimedia Commons users .
#Text=Cutting down of tree flares up Lebanese violence
#Text=After a rare clash between Israeli and Lebanese forces over the cutting down of a tree near the border of the two countries , it appears that all sides are attempting to restore peace .
#Text=The skirmish started after an Israeli soldier started cutting down a tree that has the capability to provide cover for Lebanese infiltrators .
#Text=Israel has stated that they clear the border of underbrush weekly .
#Text=After the tree was cut down , the Lebanese army started firing .
#Text=The Lebanese were allegedly aiming at a base nearby , and the resulting skirmish killed a senior Israeli military officer , a Lebanese journalist , and two Lebanese army soldiers .
#Text=The United Nations peacekeeping force in south Lebanon has stated that Israel was operating in their own territory .
#Text=However , Lebanese Information Minister Tarek Mitri said that the area of land which had the tree " [ was ]

column1: #Text=Musician and presidential candidate Wyclef Jean pictured in 2006 Image : Ali Dan-Bouzoua / Flickr .
#Text=Music star Wyclef Jean to seek Haitian presidency
#Text=According to TIME magazine , Haitian - American music star Wyclef Jean is to seek Haiti 's presidency this Thursday .

#Text=Last week Jean , who is a former member of the Fugees music group , took legal steps to run for the presidency , and Jean said in an interview that " if I ca n't take five years out to serve my country as President , then everything I 've been singing about , like equal rights , does n't mean anything .
#Text="

#Text=The Boeing 787 Dreamliner 's first flight .
#Text=Image : Dave Sizer and Altair78 .
#Text=Boeing 787 orders go negative for 2010
#Text=Aircraft company Boeing lost orders for 26 jets over the past week , according to the company 's website .
#Text=Boeing lost 15 orders for their new and long-delayed 787 Dreamliner , 10 for their Boeing 777 and one for their smaller 737 jet .
#Text=The company also gained two orders for the 737 , which makes for a net loss of 25 orders .
#Text=Boeing has n't identified the customers that cancelled their orders .
#Text=With the 15 dropped 787 orders , Boeing has lost four more orders than it gained for the aircraft this year .
#Text=Boeing has gained 28 orders for the 787 and lost 32 in 2010 .
#Text=Boeing has gained 255 orders for its lineup this year , which consists of the 737 , 747 , 767 , 777 and 787 .
#Text=229 of those orders are for the 737 jet .
#Text=Sources
#Text=Ben Mutzabaugh .
#Text=" Cancellations : Boeing 's Dreamliner orders go negative for 2010 " — USA Today , August 6 , 2010
#Text=" Boeing Dreamliner orders go negative for the year " — Seattle Times , August 5 , 2010
#Text=" Orders and Deliveries " — Boeing , August 3 , 2010
#Text=Alex Rodriguez hits 600th home run
#Text=Alex Rodriguez , baseball player for the New York Yankees , hit his 600th career home run on Wednesday .
#Text=His 600th home run was hit in Yankee Stadium against the Toronto Blue Jays .
#Text=The Yankees currently lead 5 – 1 against the Blue Jays in the game .
#Text=Yankees manager Joe Girardi said that the homer was " an amazing feat — quite an accomplishment .
